``They were there, and they were gone,'' she said. Mrs.  Barton's body was in a closet. Why didn't he just kill himself that day in Atlanta? Four people were killed in that office. Afterward, his wife and  two children were found dead in their apartment. Not one time. Leigh Ann Barton took them in. That day trader could have made as much as $400. Police and company officials immediately suspected Barton. Delawalla and eight other people were shot to death at AllTech and Momentum Securities, another day trading firm where Barton was a regular.